"{\"uid\": \"newsus.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-11-What-makes-the-2024-Paris-Olympics-so-memorable--1vXVgWaqbjG-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Hendrik Sybrandy  Copied  What helps make the Olympics so memorable are those special moments that don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t often happen in the sports we tend to watch day to day. The Paris Olympics did not disappoint on that score.  CGTN\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Hendrik Sybrandy speaks with Americans on the street to find out what stood out about this year\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Games.  For more, check out our exclusive content onCGTN Nowand subscribe to our weekly newsletter,The China Report.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"